metadata.description: "Naughty or nice? That's for Santa to decide, but with these sexy female Santas on your side, you might just sway the odds in your favor. These mischievous Mrs. Clauses are full of surprises and sure to bring some heat to your holiday season. Get your hands on one of these steamy NFTs and see if you can convince Santa to upgrade your stocking stuffers this year. But be warned: these Santas are wild, so proceed at your own risk.
metadata.name: Santas Gone Wild #1
